    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oct 1921 - Valley of the Kings - Four competing egyptologists stumble on a new discovery. A Pharaoh's tomb! However only one archaeologist can claim the find!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/f5e8f901813f39120958dc8eeee022d4.poster.avif?t=1730740725\" width=800 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/f5e8f901813f39120958dc8eeee022d4.webm?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/f5e8f901813f39120958dc8eeee022d4.mp4?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover Tombs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a tomb full of puzzle chambers. Work together or against players to solve a variety of puzzles and open each chamber door. The first player to complete the chamber wins the discovery.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Treasures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and collect treasures littered throughout the tomb’s chambers. Each treasure collected adds to your score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/6bb3bdaac0d4dadace0609ff1fbf5fca.poster.avif?t=1730740725\" width=800 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/6bb3bdaac0d4dadace0609ff1fbf5fca.webm?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/6bb3bdaac0d4dadace0609ff1fbf5fca.mp4?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exchange treasures at the mummy shop, or use them to purchase skills - higher jump, navigational aids, or more boost. Don't get too carried away though - the more you spend the less you can take back to your museum!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/879622fa4ee19fed1c2d3508bda9b73c.poster.avif?t=1730740725\" width=800 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/879622fa4ee19fed1c2d3508bda9b73c.webm?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244430/extras/879622fa4ee19fed1c2d3508bda9b73c.mp4?t=1730740725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win Alone or Co-Op</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or compete with friends to discover the secrets buried deep in the tomb.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep track of treasures gained to compete between sessions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enable &quot;Random Chambers&quot; to shuffle the tomb and play new chambers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
